Even though Eion
didn't pull the trigger.

524
00:47:37.240 --> 00:47:38.657
remember what I tell you.

525
00:47:40.907 --> 00:47:42.365
that was Alpire's plan.

526
00:47:42.615 --> 00:47:44.782
