- Pawn on D5.

537
00:49:13.199 --> 00:49:14.449
And my pawn is gone!

538
00:49:16.116 --> 00:49:20.365
We're talking global Onyx
deployment. not just national.

539
00:49:20.490 --> 00:49:21.907
I think the American
state has every

540
